Syntax: auto {parameter} 

/* YOU MAY WANT TO GO MORTAL and read mortal version for other parameters */

IMMORTAL:
success:   on = all skills will succeed or fail automatically based on nohassle
                condition.  nohassle on = auto-success, nohassle off = 
                auto-fail.
           off = mortal style success/failure.  ie. random

